Description:
A Wayland display server and X11 window manager and compositor library.

This is only used in tests.

Local Modifications:
- Implement chromium ui-controls protocol in forked chromium branch.

When updating to a new version, update the Revision above with the new commit hash,
and perform the following steps:
1. Run on_update.sh
2. Check in the generated files along with the changes for the update.
